  "sketchCode": "// Example: Relay Toggle\n// Switch a relay on and off every 2 seconds.\n// Uses external 5V power supply for the relay coil.\n\nint relayPin = 7;\n\nvoid setup() {\n  pinMode(relayPin, OUTPUT);\n}\n\nvoid loop() {\n  digitalWrite(relayPin, HIGH);\n  delay(2000);\n  digitalWrite(relayPin, LOW);\n  delay(2000);\n}\n",
